name: Swissgraffiti Graffiti 2 - Swissgraffiti.ch
description:
Swissgraffiti.ch is a "proof of authenticity" and "identity protection" service for graffiti artists (We also collect and sell NFT's.). SwissGraffiti has verified that the artist can prove that the artworks were created by him.

At Swissgraffiti, we believe that graffiti can finally arrive in the art world through NFT's.
